HAI 1.2
BTW Simple array test without string interpolation

BTW Create array with literals
VAR numbers ITZ [10, 20, 30]

BTW Access and display
VISIBLE numbers[0]
VISIBLE numbers[1]
VISIBLE numbers[2]

BTW Assignment
numbers[1] = 25
VISIBLE numbers[1]

BTW Variable index
VAR i ITZ 0
VISIBLE numbers[i]

BTW Length (access metadata directly)
VAR len ITZ numbers'Z __length
VISIBLE len

BTW Empty array
VAR empty ITZ []
VAR empty_len ITZ empty'Z __length
VISIBLE empty_len

KTHXBYE
